column5: UNP nice short covering rally in the AM but now up against Fib resistance with a sell signal on the hourly chart and a declining 5 dma A bear flag has formed on the 5 min chart so a pullback to VWAP or a lower support level is likely before the close Without some positive Mexico news a retracement to the recent lows should be anticipated
